---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="认知架构与深度思考"
  description="我对 AI、Web3 及投资逻辑的底层拆解。内容同步自 Notion 知识库。AI与杠杆、Web3思考、第一性原理。"
>

<div class="pt-28 pb-20 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">

    <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors mb-10 group text-sm font-medium">
      <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"></path></svg>
      返回首页
    </a>

    <div class="mb-16 text-center md:text-left">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4 tracking-tight">认知架构与深度思考 <span class="text-emerald-500">.</span> <span class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-500">(My MOE)</span></h1>
      <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg max-w-2xl">
        这里记录我对 AI、Web3 及投资逻辑的底层拆解。内容同步自我的 Notion 知识库。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

      <!-- AI与杠杆 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900/50 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/5 rounded-[2rem] p-8 hover:border-purple-500/50 hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-all duration-300 group flex flex-col hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-purple-400 mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 fill-none stroke-current" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.5 2.75a3.25 3.25 0 00-1.15 6.29c-.19.53-.3 1.1-.3 1.71 0 1.2.42 2.3 1.13 3.17-.9.73-1.48 1.85-1.48 3.08 0 2.23 1.9 4.03 4.25 4.03h1.3c2.35 0 4.25-1.8 4.25-4.03 0-1.23-.58-2.35-1.48-3.08.71-.87 1.13-1.97 1.13-3.17 0-.61-.11-1.18-.3-1.71A3.25 3.25 0 0014.5 2.75" />
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 7v2M10.5 11h3M10 18h4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">AI与杠杆 <span class="text-sm font-normal text-slate-500 block mt-1">AI Productivity Experiments</span></h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-1">
          利用 AI 工具链重构个体工作流。
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.notion.so/AI-2d834d7cc4e98015af4ce3f3ab20fb8f?source=copy_link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white hover:bg-purple-500/10 hover:border-purple-500/30 transition-all">阅读文章 &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Web3思考 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900/50 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/5 rounded-[2rem] p-8 hover:border-amber-500/50 hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-all duration-300 group flex flex-col hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-amber-500/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-amber-400 mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 fill-none stroke-current" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 2L4 14h7l-1 8 10-14h-7l1-6z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Web3思考 <span class="text-sm font-normal text-slate-500 block mt-1">Web3 & Asset Narratives</span></h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-1">
          探索加密时代的叙事与投资逻辑。
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.notion.so/Web3-2d834d7cc4e98094b6f5d42c8f9d11be?source=copy_link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white hover:bg-amber-500/10 hover:border-amber-500/30 transition-all">阅读文章 &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <!-- 第一性原理 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900/50 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/5 rounded-[2rem] p-8 hover:border-emerald-500/50 hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-all duration-300 group flex flex-col hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 fill-none stroke-current" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 19a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12z"></path>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 5V3a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v16"></path>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 9h8M8 13h8M8 17h6"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">第一性原理 <span class="text-sm font-normal text-slate-500 block mt-1">First Principles Thinking</span></h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-8 flex-1">
          聚焦长期不变的价值，用第一性原理过好人生
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.notion.so/2d834d7cc4e98067bbaced0eba7bab78?source=copy_link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white hover:bg-emerald-500/10 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-all">阅读文章 &rarr;</a>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-20 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">想进一步交流这些主题？</h2>
      <a href="/connect" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-white text-slate-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-slate-200 transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 shadow-lg shadow-white/10">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path></svg>
        与我聊聊 (Let's Talk)
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</BaseLayout>
